Farlin Safety Cotton Buds (Pack of 60) Price: Rs.225

Cleaning an infant’s ear should be done with utmost care and with the cleanest fabric. Farlin brings to you the Safety Cotton Bud that has been especially designed to be used for children. These Cotton Swabs are made of superior quality cotton that is skin friendly. These double tipped Farlin Cotton Buds come with paper stems that are strong and firm. The buds are designed with a two-level thickness where the tip is thinner than the base. This feature of the Farlin Safety Cotton Bud makes sure that the bud does not go deep into your tiny tot’s little ear even by mistake.

You can use this Farlin Safety Bud to clean and dry your baby’s delicate skin. The absorbent cotton fibers will easily and effectively soak up all dirt and water from the ear
column13:
navel or nose. Though gentle and soft make sure that your little one does not use the cotton swabs without your strict supervision. Always assist children to use cotton swabs to clean their ears to prevent mishaps.

\xa0

'desc': [u'

Farlin Free-drop Powder Puff (Pink) Price: Rs.210

Dusting powder on a baby’s body after bathing him or after his nappy change will keep his skin dry and free of rashes. To apply the powder evenly all over the body a powder puff is usually used. Farlin’s Free Drop Powder Puff has been designed in a very progressive way so that it gives maximum utility. A built-in powder case will allow you to deposit the baby powder into it. This will provide continuous powder without having to dip the puff in the powder every now and then.

The puff on this Farlin Free Drop is made of soft feather like fabric\xa0that will brush your bundle of joy’s skin gently and smoothly. This soft material used will control the amount of powder falling out from the powder case and thus help you in applying an even layer. With this Farlin Free Drop Powder Puff you can conveniently dust a fine layer of powder onto your darling’s body and make him feel fresh and fragrant.

']

Farlin Paper Stem Cotton Buds (Pack of 100) Price: Rs.160

Cleaning and drying an infant’s ear and navel after bathing is necessary to keep them safe from infections. As a newborn’s skin is fragile and tender utmost care should be taken while cleaning the skin especially inside the ear and around the navel. Sterile and clean fabrics should be used for cleaning to avoid contaminations. The Farlin Paper Stem Cotton Buds are made of 100 per cent superior quality cotton. These double tipped cotton swabs are gentle and ideal to clean your bundle of joy’s delicate skin. The high grade cotton will easily absorb all moisture and help in keep the baby’s ear clean and hygienic.

The paper stem is pliable enough to adjust to the curved contours of your tiny tot’s ear. The paper stem also makes these Cotton Swabs from Farlin environment-friendly.\xa0 These Paper Stem Cotton Buds from Farlin are suitable for newborns and older children alike. Always assist your little one when cleaning her ears. Make sure that your children do not use the cotton swabs in their ears or nose without your strict supervision.

column14:
'desc': [u'

Farlin Fish Nail Clipper Price: Rs.297

Infant’s nails are soft but they still have to be trimmed to avoid dirt accumulation and to prevent the child from hurting himself. The Safety Scissors or the Fish Nail Clipper from Farlin is an adorable nail trimmer that comes in the shape of a fish. This Nail Clipper has a special design that allows you to collect the nails as you clip them. This feature will help you in preventing clipped nails getting shattered all over the place. There is a nail buff at the bottom of this Farlin Nail Clipper with which you can easily and effectively polish the rough edges of the nails. Make sure you buff the nails to prevent sharp and rough edges that can hurt your bundle of joy.

This Farlin Fish Nail Clipper comes with an anti-skid design that will keep the clipper firmly in your hand without slipping. The plastic used on the body of this Nail Clipper from Farlin is non-toxic. The small blades used in this Nail clipper let you watch the nails clearly and hence reduces the chances of bruising your infant’s fingers.

']
